              headline:'Harper\'s official Senate Facebook page tracks his signature transportation and transit work',
              facts:'Harper — Senate president pro tempore, 2024 president of the National Conference of State Legislatures, and chair of the Senate Transportation, Public Utilities, Energy and Technology Committee — keeps an official "Wayne Harper - Utah State Senator" Facebook page for District 16 (West Jordan and Taylorsville). It is a channel for the transportation-and-transit record he is best known for: he has restructured UTA and large transit-district governance and modernized how Utah funds roads and transit, the work that makes him the chamber\'s leading voice on growth and mobility.',
              why:'As the Wasatch Front\'s population surges, how Utah governs and funds its transit systems shapes daily commutes across Salt Lake County. Harper\'s page is a verifiable, first-person record of how the Legislature\'s top transportation voice frames the UTA-reform and funding work his profile documents — useful secondary context alongside his official record.',
