              facts:'Pierucci — House Majority Whip, chair of the House Education Committee, and one of the youngest members of House leadership — keeps an official "Representative Candice B. Pierucci" Facebook page she describes as a place to "update my constituents and engage in policy discussions" for Herriman and Riverton. It is a channel for the education record at the center of her agenda: she was the chief sponsor of Utah\'s "Utah Fits All" school-choice scholarship and has since carried bills to reform and tighten the program.',
