              facts:'Rep. Mike Flood of Nebraska\'s 1st District held a town hall at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln in August 2025, broadcast statewide by Nebraska Public Media, where he took extended questions from a large, often hostile audience. Pressed on health care, Flood said he believed the 2025 budget-and-tax law "protects Medicaid for the future" and stood by its Medicaid provisions.',
